%%{init: {"themeVariables": {"fontSize": "18px", "fontFamily": "Arial"}, "sequence": {"actorFontSize": 18, "messageFontSize": 17}}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    actor Browser as Student / Browser
    participant Backend as FastAPI + Socket.IO
    participant Session as Session workspace
    participant Build as SBT / chiseltest
    participant Processor as LivePipelineTest / Chisel processor
    participant Bridge as ChiselBridge

    Browser->>Backend: Upload project src folder
    Backend->>Backend: Filter files and detect course level
    Backend-->>Browser: Accepted sources and system BinaryFile
    Browser->>Backend: Compile with selected BinaryFile
    Backend->>Session: Stage scaffold, Scala sources, and BinaryFile
    Backend->>Build: Launch controlled test suite
    Build->>Processor: Elaborate processor and generate VCD
    Processor-->>Bridge: Open TCP endpoint and initial snapshot
    Bridge-->>Backend: Initial processor state
    Backend-->>Browser: Compilation succeeded
    loop Each requested cycle
        Browser->>Backend: Initialize or step
        Backend->>Bridge: Forward command
        Bridge->>Processor: Advance one clock cycle
        Processor-->>Bridge: JSON debug snapshot
        Bridge-->>Backend: Raw processor state
        Backend-->>Browser: Decoded snapshot and cycle log
    end
